@startuml
actor Agent
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Rate Limiter" as RL
participant "Event Store" as ES
participant "Blockchain" as BC

Agent -> API: POST /consume (x402 payment)
API -> RL: check rate limit
RL --> API: allowed
API -> ES: append ResourceConsumed event
API -> BC: verify x402 payment
BC --> API: payment confirmed
API --> Agent: 200 OK (receipt)
@enduml
